&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue is a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5912&quot; title=&quot;locking flaw generates logged errors&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5912&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5912&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but for Lustre 2.5.3. Could you provide a backport of &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/12731/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/12731/&lt;/a&gt; ?&lt;/p&gt;</description>
